comments: "By having to press down, it kept scrolling down my screen. I don&quotechart know if this was intentional, but it made it so I could only read the line for about half a second. "

"I think I got better, took me a little bit to get I was judging the first sentence as the TF. For whatever reason I expected the first thing you told me to be true, and I should judge the 2nd. Not exactly sure why, but that would have felt more natural to me."
"The timer was kind of short. I also would occasionally forget to hold down the down button and would miss the first sentence so this task presented an honest but pleasant challenge to me."
"Took a while to figure it out. Also, many times I hit false when I meant true."
